==Trivia==
*Although mithril seeds can be planted underwater in the [[Mogre Camp]] and the [[Underwater Tunnel]], players are unable to plant mithril seeds [[Underwater|underwater off Fossil Island]]. Attempting to do so results in the message {{RSFont|It's just a little too damp for you to plant your flowers here.}} appearing in chat. Previously, the text {{RSFont|Are you trying to drown your flowers?}} appeared.

